About

I'm a veteran journalist who has made a living cutting through the noise, whether it's as an editor at Axios, a freelance reporter or a storyteller for startups. I've worked for some of the largest publications in the country and for places you've never heard of, which gives me a unique frame of reference for packaging stories and content. The one constant? Elevating the work of the people around me.
